sSemantic\/ElevationCompositeSemanticTokens\/none","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"none","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ElevationCompositeSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic018ElevationCompositeB5Tokena"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"none","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSTokensSemantic/documentation/OUDSTokensSemantic/ElevationCompositeSemanticTokens":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/ElevationCompositeSemanticTokens","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This is a group of semantic tokens for "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"elevations"}]},{"type":"text","text":", but only "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"composite tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"There are splitted and not declared in "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/ElevationSemanticTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" as the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tokenator"}]},{"type":"text","text":" tool parsing "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Figma"}]},{"type":"text","text":" JSON to Swift code is not able to manage them."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Thus we need to declare them in another file to prevent them to be erased."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It declares in fact box shadows effects."}],"title":"ElevationCompositeSemanticTokens","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ElevationCompositeSemanticTokens"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/elevationcompositesemantictokens","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ElevationCompositeSemanticTokens"}]},"ic_design_token_figma_semantic.png":{"alt":null,"identifier":"ic_design_token_figma_semantic.png","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/ic_design_token_figma_semantic.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image"},"doc://OUDSTokensSemantic/documentation/OUDSTokensSemantic/MultipleElevationCompositeRawToken":{"title":"MultipleElevationCompositeRawToken","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleElevationCompositeRawToken","url":"\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/multipleelevationcompositerawtoken","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Semantic tokens which will wrap a combination of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ElevationCompositeRawToken"},{"type":"text","text":" depending to color scheme (i.e. light mode or dark mode)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Kind of composite token with multiple values, but not named “composite” because this word is already used in the design system."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Allows to gather the multiple-value tokens from "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Figma"}]},{"type":"text","text":" inside one object."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If an elevation token exists with its value depending to the color scheme, it must be packed in such ``MultipleElevationCompositeRawToken`"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MultipleElevationCompositeRawToken","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MultipleElevationCompositeRawToken","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OUDSTokensSemantic/documentation/OUDSTokensSemantic/ElevationCompositeSemanticToken":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/ElevationCompositeSemanticToken","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Basically an elevationcomposite  semantic token, used mainly for box shadow, is a pair of elevation composite raw tokens used depending to the color scheme."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleElevationCompositeRawToken","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" contains "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ElevationCompositeRawToken"},{"type":"text","text":" objects for light and dark modes, which contains "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ElevationRawToken"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ColorRawToken"},{"type":"text","text":" values."}],"title":"ElevationCompositeSemanticToken","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ElevationCompositeSemanticToken","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/elevationcompositesemantictoken","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"typealias","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ElevationCompositeSemanticToken","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OUDSTokensSemantic/documentation/OUDSTokensSemantic/ElevationSemanticTokens":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/ElevationSemanticTokens","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This is a group of semantic tokens for "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"elevations"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It defines all elevation semantic tokens a theme must have ("},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/ElevationXSemanticToken"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/ElevationYSemanticToken"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/ElevationBlurSemanticToken"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/ElevationColorSemanticToken"},{"type":"text","text":")."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However the composite tokens (here for box shadows) are defined in "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/ElevationCompositeSemanticTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" because the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tokenator"}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is not able to generate them yet, and they must be defined elsewhere to not be deleted."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Any elevation semantic token must be declared there (except "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/ElevationCompositeSemanticTokens"},{"type":"text","text":")"}],"title":"ElevationSemanticTokens","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ElevationSemanticTokens"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/elevationsemantictokens","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ElevationSemanticTokens"}]},"doc://OUDSTokensSemantic/documentation/OUDSTokensSemantic":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"These "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tokens"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" can be used mainly for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":" to apply some style and configuration values ; today "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component tokens"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"components"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" are not defined yet."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"They can be seen as an high level of usage with functional meanings."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_design_token_figma_semantic.png"}],"title":"Tokens for semantics"}}}